  "text": "where f x : R nx \u00d7 R ny \u00d7 R m \u2192 R nx and f y : R nx \u00d7 R ny \u00d7 R m \u2192 R ny are smooth mappings. [CITATION_1] Assume that the input signal vector u : R + \u2192 R m is such that all trajectories of the system are bounded. Find, if possible, mappings F : R n \u03be \u00d7 R ny \u00d7 R m \u2192 R n \u03be and G :",
